expectation e_2ea25e8cda4d2d78 target=project subject=- status=accepted source="human:maintainer" title="litterae keeps expectations explicit" detail="litterae should keep project expectations in an authored expectations.susu sidecar so implementation evidence and intent can be reviewed together.";
expectation e_ee705788dc2f4a20 target=project subject=- status=proposed source="human:maintainer" title="litterae documents primary workflows" detail="litterae should describe the business or product workflows that matter most, then link those expectations to observed files, symbols, or workflows as evidence improves.";
expectation e_0cf9ce3bfb208414 target=project subject=- status=proposed source="human:maintainer" title="litterae records verification evidence" detail="litterae should record how important expectations are checked, such as tests, CI runs, manual reviews, policy checks, runtime traces, or release approvals.";
